{"type": "article", "id": 38805, "title": "MYKITA的概念眼镜，就是一条可以折的金属｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-15T00:03:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 23438, "name": "Atelier-D"}, {"id": 27564, "name": "Peleg Design"}, {"id": 29618, "name": "MYKITA"}, {"id": 38534, "name": "RELVÃOKELLERMANN"}, {"id": 38535, "name": "Watermark Design"}, {"id": 38536, "name": "Adam Lister"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 248, "image": "img/article/article_show/201703150803362QGybEprSnRhktqs.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>8 bit paintings by Adam Lister</h3><p>如果你喜欢让人回忆起老式电子游戏的 8 比特低像素风格，不妨看看美国艺术家 <a href=\"https://adam-lister-gallery.myshopify.com/\">Adam Lister</a> 对一系列世界名画和雕塑的再创作。在这些水彩画中，原作本身的细节被各式各样的像素图形所取代，虽然看起来有些杂乱，但依然保持了很高的辨识度。目前 Lister 的作品正在纽约的 <a href=\"http://catalystgallery.com/\">Catalyst Gallery</a> 展出，展期将持续到 3 月 26 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214820gKRpsvk3Yna2H6yo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593023\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214820YP3brTpxOgNifMUZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769767\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214820ACoSrbQWs53Ouztn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.270930\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214821iFVJB7pYh98QoIzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.289535\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017031421481947bMnITNJyip5Pfu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772093\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>信物 by Memento</h3><p>为了体现职人所持有的坚持以及对细节的考究，来自台湾的设计团队 Memento 以六种职人所使用的道具为灵感，设计了一套名为“信物”的拆信刀组作为职人的“信念延伸”。整套“信物”包含云尺、羽毛笔、扳手、针、剪刀以及作为隐藏版的凿刀，并配有采用荷兰布裱制的外盒。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/memento\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为新台币 1499 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703142149372yrn9iYaVG7QIvCh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214937DEoIfiSTYaH1Qb4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214937LSMjOIU6HXmtbqJw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703142149375pyWFsL1fqn2AvXR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214938wyA1VaRWqiIoD0re.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214938Fvd76CfPEI4MNZ0g.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.456667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Soap Opera by Peleg Design</h3><p>还记得那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30229.html\">专供海绵休息的小床</a>吗？同样致力于创造生活趣味的以色列设计品牌 <a href=\"https://www.peleg-design.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Peleg Design</a> 最近也推出了一个有着相似概念的收纳工具。Soap Opera 的外形就像是一个坐在浴缸中高歌的歌唱家，她的发型完全取决于插在小柱子上的海绵和钢丝清洁球，浴缸则刚好用来接住多余的肥皂水。它将于 3 月 27 日正式发售，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.peleg-design.com/shop/soap-opera.html\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">链接</a>预订，售价为 13.50 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017031421495340sehTiDn8Yd6C23.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214953yI6TzwuVjkGdNCWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314214953POCQ6eV54rcZUJvD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Oblika Puzzle by Atelier-D</h3><p>凭借着对手工技术的热爱，加拿大设计师 Jonathan Dorthe 创立了名为 <a href=\"http://www.atelier-d.ca/\">Atelier-D</a> 的设计品牌，专门经营各类融合了建筑元素的手工艺品。这款以几何图案为主题打造的拼图 Oblika 是它的最新产品，共包含 22 块木制拼图，可以组合成一系列建筑轮廓。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.atelier-d.ca/shop/oblika-puzzle\">购买链接</a>，售价为 50 加元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215016zUHtpOM564WDGEIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664011\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215016IRnVdUDrTCskj8Og.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215017fwdsKcxJOEPhWkaG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215016vYUjP7JTazqlMpLg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Frame by RELVÃOKELLERMANN &amp; MYKITA</h3><p>你见过只需要一条细长的金属板就能拼好的眼镜吗？为了削减眼镜制作过程中产生的浪费，德国眼镜品牌 <a href=\"https://mykita.com/en#\">MYKITA</a> 和设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.relvaokellermann.com/\">RELVÃOKELLERMANN</a> 联手推出了这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.relvaokellermann.com/project/frame-lab/\">Frame</a> 的概念眼镜。每一副眼镜的镜框都被精简成了 2D 的版本，因此只需一张金属板就能雕刻出大量的镜框，随后再根据需要扭曲定型为 3D 形态，整个过程甚至不需要螺丝额外固定，进一步减少了制作成本。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215104ILrxaMTnPWJ3Qwh4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.947656\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215104ymEukvq5xbLjeMFC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215104SymlICBAPF2eGoKs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.337037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215105Hh5vp2TjkUwoxZMd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Jake Busching Wines by Watermark Design</h3><p>采用有机种植法的美国葡萄酒庄 Jake Busching Wines 最近完成了一小批维欧尼（Viognier）和品丽珠（Cabernet Franc）葡萄酒的生产，为了强调“有机”和“自然”的概念，负责包装设计的 <a href=\"https://designbywatermark.com/\">Watermark Design</a> 利用水彩和分割标签的粗糙边缘模仿出压榨过程中汁水流淌而下的效果，简单却很讨巧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215201Yw6HStjh92RECz1y.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703142152025fUWHQIdmnhG8s96.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170314215202robGZJtSaLVhpAFT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}